          <outline text="I see he's working on the WordPress RSS Cloud plugin" created="Mon, 27 Apr 2026 16:18:04 GMT" type="link" url="https://andrewshell.org/2026/04/working-on-the-rss-cloud-wordpress-plugin/"/>
          <outline text="The one we figured out a few months ago wasn't working, so I wrote a workaround for it 😃" created="Mon, 27 Apr 2026 16:18:23 GMT"/>
          <outline text="I'll have to get in touch with him to see if we can collaborate" created="Mon, 27 Apr 2026 16:19:31 GMT"/>
        </outline>
        <outline text="Dave's podcast" created="Mon, 27 Apr 2026 16:14:22 GMT" type="outline">
          <outline text="It's the end of my day here, so real quick..." created="Mon, 27 Apr 2026 16:14:36 GMT"/>
          <outline text="Yeah, I think you can release it" created="Mon, 27 Apr 2026 16:14:50 GMT"/>
          <outline text="It rambles, but all the pieces fit together" created="Mon, 27 Apr 2026 16:14:59 GMT"/>
          <outline text="I like the part about AI reducing stress when coming back to a project, I haven't heard that anyplace else" created="Mon, 27 Apr 2026 16:15:10 GMT"/>
        </outline>
      </outline>
      <outline text="April 23" created="Thu, 23 Apr 2026 15:23:58 GMT" type="calendarDay" name="23">
        <outline text="Testing the site-id changes" created="Thu, 23 Apr 2026 15:23:59 GMT" type="outline">
          <outline text="I don't run my local WordPress test environment often enough to remember how it works " created="Thu, 23 Apr 2026 15:24:09 GMT">
            <outline text="Good thing Codex can remind me 😃" created="Thu, 23 Apr 2026 16:26:05 GMT"/>
          </outline>
        </outline>
        <outline text="It's been quiet on here?" created="Thu, 23 Apr 2026 16:15:49 GMT" type="outline">
