          <outline text="Wordpress hosting, I need to set up the API on the WordPress side to be able to create sites programmatically " created="Tue, 10 Mar 2026 16:35:00 GMT">
            <outline text="I had found a solution but hadn't tried it out yet" created="Tue, 10 Mar 2026 16:38:43 GMT"/>
            <outline text="I'll get right on it. " created="Tue, 10 Mar 2026 16:39:24 GMT"/>
          </outline>
        </outline>
      </outline>
